reviewText: I just got my order of Season 4 today and I am so excited! I can't wait to watch the two episodes revolving around my crush at the time (Jennie Kwan). This show really is a great representation of my childhood. I was so peaceful, free-spirited and fun-loving growing up and really loved this show. I wanted to meet great people like the cast, but it just never happened. I just hope that my future children love this show too. Great cast, voices, and stories! This season should be picked up by real fans of the show. The more you buy it, the sooner season 5 is released! 90's kid forever! Glad that I own all seasons available through DVD. Memories :)
summary: Don't wake me up if I'm Dreamin'..California Dreams
